---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
---

<Layout title="About | Never Stop Learning" description="About the Never Stop Learning platform">
  <div class="flex min-h-svh flex-col">
    <header class="border-b px-6 py-4">
      <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/never-stop-learning" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Never Stop Learning</span>
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/never-stop-learning/courses" class="text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground">Courses</a>
          <a href="/never-stop-learning/about" class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">About</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1 px-6 py-12">
      <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Never Stop Learning</h1>

        <section class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground">
          <p>
            Never Stop Learning is a free, open-source educational platform built for developers and lifelong learners. The goal is simple: provide clear, well-structured courses on topics that matter.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you're picking up your first programming language or preparing for a system design interview, this platform aims to give you practical knowledge without the noise.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What Makes This Different</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
            <li>No paywalls. All content is free and open.</li>
            <li>Content is concise and to the point.</li>
            <li>Courses are organized by difficulty level.</li>
            <li>Built with modern web technologies (Astro, React, Tailwind).</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Tech Stack</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground">
            This site is built with Astro, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui. It's hosted on GitHub Pages and the source code is fully available.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contributing</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground">
            Contributions are welcome. If you'd like to add a course, fix a typo, or suggest an improvement, feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request on GitHub.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t px-6 py-6 text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      Never Stop Learning &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()}
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
